definition: pincers/pliers/tongs/claw (of animal)/to grasp with pincers/to pinch/to clamp/to restrain/to restrict/to gag

sentences.english: How likely will it be that I’ll need forceps during delivery?
sentences.chinese: 什麼樣的情況下，在生產中我會需要用到產鉗？

sentences.english: They also used forceps for difficult births.
sentences.chinese: 他們還在難產的時候使用產鉗。

sentences.english: Smellie improved the forceps and wrote a bestselling practical midwifery handbook.
sentences.chinese: 斯梅利改良了產鉗，並寫下了實用的助產術手冊。

sentences.english: My friend’s ob used a vacuum extractor to help deliver her baby. Is that the same as forceps?
sentences.chinese: 我的朋友在生產時用到了真空吸引，這和產鉗一樣嗎？
